    "diffSummary": "Added text sending. command/ gains a send_message command that validates thread_id/text, looks up an already-authenticated session from ListenerState (now a HashMap<AccountId, Arc<API>> populated on start_listening), and delegates to zalo::send_text — credentials are never re-sent from the UI. The frontend adds a composer (thread id + message) that calls send_message and shows the returned message id. Verified live: one real text message was delivered to the authorized recipient (resolved by phone) and Zalo returned a non-empty message id; the attested smoke sidecar was scanned and contains no credential values or recipient phone number.",
    "changedFiles": [
